These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, scooter
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, balloon-flower
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, thriller
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, social-worker
City: boston, miami
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, folk
2 different games are played: scrabble, bridge
1. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
5. the person playing bridge is the person watching thriller movies##1
6. the social-worker is the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Transport      | scooter        | boat |
| Flower          | balloon-flower  | poppy     |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller    | drama         |
| Job           | analyst    | social-worker |
| City   | boston  | miami     |
| Music-Genre           | folk      | soul    |
| Game         | bridge | scrabble          |

